      "writtenOn": "2021-01-13T20:20:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The spec allows float loops, so start and delta are directly extracted from the loop terms. count is the actual number of iterations to run, so it\u0027s always integral. I used double to cover the range of possible inputs over both 32-bit integers, and float. (vs. having a union and type-tag)",
